@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_skclre(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.94 - tmp + 0.90)) - v2)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.41 * v1 + 0.36)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v1 + 0.12) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.64)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.97 * v2 + 0.16)) * v0)
    v0 = wp.abs(v1)
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = 0.99
    data[tid] = v0
